OL,7,FA man was allegedly scalded with
OL,8,Fboiling water and stabbed repeatedly
OL,9,Ffor disliking a woman on Facebook, a
OL,10,Fcourt has been told.
OL,12,FPolice claimed the victim was also
OL,13,Fbound, gagged and forced to strip off
OL,14,Fafter letting two suspected assailants
OL,15,Finto his home in Comber, Co Down.
OL,17,FHe lay there badly wounded for more
OL,18,Fthan 24 hours without seeking help due
OL,19,Fto fears his family would be harmed if
OL,20,Fhe contacted police, a judge was told.
