OL,7,FDetails emerged as 32-year-old David
OL,8,FSmyth was refused compassionate bail
OL,9,Fon charges of taking part in the
OL,10,Fattack in the early hours of March 20.
OL,12,FSmyth, with an address at Reaville
OL,13,FPark in Dundonald, is accused of
OL,14,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,15,Fintent, false imprisonment, theft of
OL,16,Fclothing and possessing offensive
OL,17,Fweapons - namely a knife and kettle.
