OL,7,FBelfast Magistrates' Court heard the
OL,8,Fvictim agreed to let the defendant and
OL,9,Fa female co-accused visit his
OL,10,Fapartment in the Orange Hall Lane area
OL,11,Fwhile he was there drinking with a
OL,12,Ffriend.
OL,14,FThe woman, wearing a snood with a
OL,15,Fskeleton logo, and Smyth began
OL,16,Fstriking him after they were let into
OL,17,Fthe property, according to his account.
OL,19,FHe stated that he was tied up with
OL,20,Fblack cables as the attack continued.
