OL,7,FSmyth allegedly stabbed him multiple
OL,8,Ftimes with a kitchen knife, gagged him
OL,9,Fwith a microfibre cloth and poured
OL,10,Fboiling water from a kettle over him.
OL,12,FAn investigating detective told the
OL,13,Fcourt: "While the assault was taking
OL,14,Fplace (the woman) took the victim's
OL,15,Fphone, scrolled through it and
OL,16,Freportedly said 'do you f****** like
OL,17,Fme now?'."
