OL,7,FHe claimed the victim was made to
OL,8,Fstrip off and put his clothes and
OL,9,Fphone in a plastic bag which the
OL,10,Fassailants took with them.
OL,12,FBefore leaving the apartment Smyth
OL,13,Fallegedly warned the man's mother and
OL,14,Fgrandmother would be harmed if he
OL,15,Finformed the PSNI.
OL,17,F"The threat of harm caused the victim
OL,18,Fto lie in bed for over 24 hours
OL,19,Fwithout contacting police or seeking
OL,20,Fmedical attention out of fear," the
OL,21,Fdetective said.
