OL,7,FHis mother alerted the authorities
OL,8,Fafter discovering him "in a bad state"
OL,9,Fat the apartment on March 21.
OL,11,FHe was taken to the Ulster Hospital to
OL,12,Fbe treated for burns to his body,
OL,13,Fnasal bone fractures, face and leg
OL,14,Fwounds, and a 3cm deep laceration to
OL,15,Fthe side of his head.
OL,17,FThe man named both defendants as the
OL,18,Falleged assailants.
