OL,7,F"When asked why he was attacked, the
OL,8,Fvictim stated that he was friends with
OL,9,F(the female co-accused) on Facebook
OL,10,Fand had been saying things online
OL,11,Fabout her not being a nice person and
OL,12,Fthat he didn't like her," the
OL,13,Fdetective disclosed.
OL,15,FThe court heard police obtained CCTV
OL,16,Ffootage of the two defendants at a
OL,17,Fpetrol station in Comber a number of
OL,18,Fhours after the assault.
